text:
SAN JOAQUIN COUNTY ( CBS13) — The San Joaquin County Office Of Emergency Services reports that a levee int he White House Slough State Wildlife Area near Lodi has broken.
ThOfficials say there is no threat to other areas asked that people be careful walking around the area.
CBS13 will have further details as they become available.
